UPDATE `users` SET `vFirstName` = 'Dona', `vLastName` = 'Paula', `vProfileImage` = '978307200_5fb4e1ba539f8.png', `dDob` = '1995-11-18', `tAddress` = '', `vCity` = 'Roswell', `dLatitude` = '', `dLongitude` = '', `vStateName` = 'Georgia', `vZipCode` = '', `dtUpdatedAt` = NOW(), `vUserName` = '', `vMobileNo` = '', `vGender` = 'Female', `iAge` = '25' WHERE `iUserId` = '8' AND `eStatus` IN('Active')

SELECT `u`.`iUserId` AS `u_user_id`,`u`.`vFirstName` AS `u_first_name`,`u`.`vLastName` AS `u_last_name`,`u`.`vUserName` AS `u_user_name`,`u`.`vEmail` AS `u_email`,`u`.`vMobileNo` AS `u_mobile_no`,`u`.`vProfileImage` AS `u_profile_image`,`u`.`dDob` AS `u_dob`,`u`.`eSocialLoginType` AS `u_social_login_type`,`u`.`vSocialLoginId` AS `u_social_login_id`,`u`.`tAddress` AS `u_address`,`u`.`vCity` AS `u_city`,`u`.`dLatitude` AS `u_latitude`,`u`.`dLongitude` AS `u_longitude`,`u`.`iStateId` AS `u_state_id`,`u`.`vStateName` AS `u_state`,`u`.`vZipCode` AS `u_zip_code`,`u`.`ePushNotify` AS `u_push_notify`,`u`.`vAccessToken` AS `u_access_token`,`u`.`eDeviceType` AS `u_device_type`,`u`.`vDeviceModel` AS `u_device_model`,`u`.`vDeviceOS` AS `u_device_os`,`u`.`vDeviceToken` AS `u_device_token`,`u`.`eStatus` AS `u_status`,`u`.`dtAddedAt` AS `u_added_at`,`u`.`dtUpdatedAt` AS `u_updated_at`,`u`.`eEmailVerified` AS `u_email_verified`,`ms`.`vState` AS `ms_state`,`u`.`eOneTimeTransaction` AS `e_one_time_transaction`,`u`.`tOneTimeTransaction` AS `t_one_time_transaction`,`u`.`vTermsConditionsVersion` AS `u_terms_conditions_version`,`u`.`vPrivacyPolicyVersion` AS `u_privacy_policy_version`,(concat(u.vFirstName,' ',u.vLastName)) AS email_user_name,`u`.`vGender` AS `u_gender`,`u`.`iAge` AS `u_age`,`u`.`eLogStatus` AS `u_log_status_updated`,`u`.`eIsSubscribed` AS `u_is_subscribed`,`u`.`tReceiptData` AS `u_receipt_data`,`u`.`vSubscriptionId` AS `u_subscription_id` FROM `users` AS `u` LEFT JOIN `mod_state` AS `ms` ON `u`.`iStateId` = `ms`.`iStateId` WHERE `u`.`iUserId` = '8'  LIMIT 1
